column1: Baby Barnaby's////I ordered the eggs + potatoes + biscuit + bacon
column2: and boyfriend got the famous green eggs. In my opinion
column3: the green eggs were a little runny
column4: but the flavor was great and I suppose we should've specified our preferred softness of egg. My breakfast was super filling and super satisfying
column5: and dat biscuit was amazing! NOTABLY
column6: the potatoes here are GOOD. I am used to ones that are too soft or something
column7: but these are crispy on the outside and soft and warm inside
column8: and are seasoned super well. I am SOLD.
